{"tid":573538,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"CityU就係CityU，唔係乜野CU","createTime":"2018-02-26T14:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T15:04:53.000Z","uid":135607,"like":101,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8573b1fff8fcd2c77480729560bf58223a9a30b4","tid":573538,"uid":135607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:21:20.000Z","msg":"我地城市大學全體師生咁辛苦先提升到我地既教學質素<br />\n令我校成功躋身全球大學頂尖行列 並且成為香港三大之一<br />\n點解我地CityU如今仲要自降身價 執中文大學既口水尾叫自己做CU?<br />\nCU個名根本唔配掛落我地城市大學身上<br />\n我地當刻既任務 應該係同其他人講 而家三大係 CityU HKU UST<br />\n而唔係同人講CityU係新CU 因為CU個名襯唔上我地 <br />\n我地唔應該用呢間中衰大學既簡稱 各位CityU同學明唔明白？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5182cf763c9f288b62dcb9cea13d0db7ee349339","tid":573538,"uid":4070,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:22:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"662d63665f5f2cea854391b4cef6036ace94ad25","tid":573538,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"Ching Ho Ball"},{"pid":"4b786c8483cf95df53bf16a7501dba100db935e0","tid":573538,"uid":152520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a558381decc324b6a9d11c91a728bf35ac2be6","tid":573538,"uid":152520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe52e8ca17d44ff4dfc9e80b6c08c237cc9cc8d","tid":573538,"uid":34525,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5182cf763c9f288b62dcb9cea13d0db7ee349339","tid":573538,"uid":4070,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:22:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"U like la<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62a8a1e1fe75937efa0479c1854121c03605590","tid":573538,"uid":2500